{"tid":602180,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Naspers 揸騰訊揸足17年","createTime":"2018-03-22T23:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T03:27:25.000Z","uid":80972,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"731518d9e255af8ec096db3f4110fd02884bb519","tid":602180,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:42:16.000Z","msg":"Naspers早於2001年，亦即騰訊上市前已擔任其主要股東。Naspers於當年5月以2.66億元南非蘭特（約值2.95億港元）買入騰訊46.4%的股權，在騰訊上市後被攤薄至現時約33.17%，在不計股息的情況下，其回報已高達4700倍。雖然騰訊由2006上市至今，股價漲升了594倍，Naspers仍然不為所動，一股不沽。以當年<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">騰訊招股價僅3.7元</span></strong>（其後再1拆5）計算，Naspers今次在高位沽貨幾乎是「淨賺」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當年有抽新股，好似咁醒識長揸都fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"01cdad5120e996424e4710215013a145e89e0b14","tid":602180,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:47:31.000Z","msg":"騰訊南非大股東Naspers以405港元/股價格出售持有的騰訊股份，較上一交易日收盤價折讓約7.8%。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479e48c9f850ea4a2d63fd5bfc585fd386149754","tid":602180,"uid":171878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:53:55.000Z","msg":"佢間公司的管理層同分析師真係勁 賺到盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae923cddd6b3bda451cfcd4c44ca1e362d5a995","tid":602180,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01cdad5120e996424e4710215013a145e89e0b14","tid":602180,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:47:31.000Z","msg":"騰訊南非大股東Naspers以405港元/股價格出售持有的騰訊股份，較上一交易日收盤價折讓約7.8%。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T23:55:57.000Z","msg":"點解條撚樣唔分幾十次沽 咁班好友咪唔洗輸咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600450110aed6320c209788